movie_name: Matt Baker: Our Farm in the Dales
short_description: Television presenter Matt Baker receives a call that leads him to move his wife and two children north to run his family's sheep farm in the Durham hills after his mum had a serious accident.

facts_and_links: {'Trivia': ["The first series was a major success for Channel 4's sister channel More4, quickly becoming the channel's most successful new commission. On the 23rd August 2021, Channel 4 Television announced that they have commissioned Big Circus Media to make two further 6-episode series and a Christmas special of the hit show. The show's star and executive producer Matt Baker revealed on Instagram that filming was already underway on the second series.", 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt14092120/trivia/?ref_=tt_dyk_trv']}
